=== 專業評價 ===
第三代的iPad獲得了普遍正面的評價。許多媒體贊譽高解析度的Retina顯示器和LTE通訊網路的支援（只用於部分地區）。<ref name="engadgettim"/><ref name="PCWorldreview">{{cite web | url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/252010/apple_ipad_review_the_retina_display_redefines_the_tablet.html | title=Apple iPad Review: The Retina Display Redefines the Tablet | publisher=PCWorld | date=March 16, 2012 | accessdate=March 16, 2012 | author=Perenson, Melissa | archive-date=2013-11-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105052539/http://www.pcworld.com/article/252010/apple_ipad_review_the_retina_display_redefines_the_tablet.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="MSNGadget">{{cite web | url=http://www.gadgetbox.msnbc.msn.com/technology/gadgetbox/ipad-review-its-renovation-not-revolution-463973 | title=iPad review: It's a renovation, not a revolution | publisher=MSN Gadgetbox | date=March 16, 2012 | accessdate=March 16, 2012 | author=Golijan, Rosa | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120319051441/http://www.gadgetbox.msnbc.msn.com/technology/gadgetbox/ipad-review-its-renovation-not-revolution-463973 | archivedate=2012年3月19日 }}</ref>[[Engadget|Engadget]]的提姆·史蒂芬斯（Tim Stevens）認為「如果你對於蘋果在新iPad上推出的改變不夠多而到失望，那可能是因為你還沒親眼看過新的Retina顯示器」。<ref name="engadgettim">{{cite web | url=http://www.engadget.com/2012/03/16/apple-ipad-review-2012/ | title=iPad review (2012) | publisher=Engadget | date=March 16, 2012 | accessdate=March 16, 2012 | author=Stevens, Tim | archive-date=2012-03-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323223847/http://www.engadget.com/2012/03/16/apple-ipad-review-2012/ | dead-url=no }}</ref> 

[[All_Things_Digital|All Things Digital]]的[[華特·莫思柏|華特·莫思柏]]（Walt Mossberg）表示第三代的iPad「有著目前為止我在行動裝置上看過最令人震撼的螢幕」、「從2010年首次推出以來，iPad就是地球上最棒的平板電腦。而這部全新、第三代的款式，iPad依然穩坐王位」。<ref name="MossbergReview">{{cite web | url=http://allthingsd.com/20120314/new-ipad-a-million-more-pixels-than-hdtv/ | title=New iPad: A Million More Pixels Than HDTV | publisher=[[All_Things_Digital|All Things Digital]] | date=March 14, 2012 | accessdate=March 17, 2012 | author=[[Walter_Mossberg|Mossberg, Walter]] | archive-date=2012-03-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323203148/http://allthingsd.com/20120314/new-ipad-a-million-more-pixels-than-hdtv/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

雖然第三代iPad在推出時獲得了普遍正面的評價，但海外市場的消費者卻很快地發現，新款iPad在支援Verizon和AT&T（700MHz、1.7GHz）以外的LTE頻率上出現問題。除了美國以外，其他國家都是使用800MHz、1.8GHz和2.6GHz的頻率，新款iPad將無法連接上美國以外的LTE網路。<ref name="CnetWorld">{{cite web | url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-30686_3-57395687-266/will-4g-lte-devices-ever-roam-internationally/ | title=Will 4G LTE devices ever roam internationally? | publisher=Cnet | date=March 12, 2012 | accessdate=March 21, 2012 | author=Reardon, Marguerite | archive-date=2012-08-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120811014744/http://news.cnet.com/8301-30686_3-57395687-266/will-4g-lte-devices-ever-roam-internationally/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="iPad3Aust">{{cite web | url=http://www.itwire.com/your-it-news/mobility/53527-the-ipad-3-hotspot-notspot | title=The iPad 3 hotspot notspot | publisher=iTWire | date=March 20, 2012 | accessdate=March 21, 2012 | author=Zaharov-Reutt, Alex | archive-date=2012-03-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120322214035/http://www.itwire.com/your-it-news/mobility/53527-the-ipad-3-hotspot-notspot | dead-url=no }}</ref>

許多使用者也反應了第三代iPad有著機身溫度提高的現象，尤其是在執行3D遊戲之後。熱探測影像的測試發現，新iPad的机身溫度最高可達華氏116度（約攝氏46度），雖然在最高溫時並不會造成使用者在握持上的不適。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://crave.cnet.co.uk/laptops/apples-new-ipad-overheats-irate-users-complain-50007375/ | title=Apple's new iPad overheats, irate users complain | publisher=CNET | date=March 19, 2012 | accessdate=March 22, 2012 | author=Andrew Williams | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120322040414/http://crave.cnet.co.uk/laptops/apples-new-ipad-overheats-irate-users-complain-50007375/ | archive-date=2012-03-22 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://beta.techradar.com/news/computing/apple/new-ipad-caught-running-at-116-degrees-fahrenheit-1072568 | title=New iPad caught running at 116 degrees Fahrenheit | publisher=TechRadar | date=March 22, 2012 | accessdate=March 22, 2012 | author=Smith, Chris | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323211545/http://beta.techradar.com/news/computing/apple/new-ipad-caught-running-at-116-degrees-fahrenheit-1072568 | archivedate=2012年3月23日 }}</ref><ref name="Creports">{{cite web | url=http://news.consumerreports.org/electronics/2012/03/our-test-finds-new-ipad-hits-116-degrees-while-running-games.html | title=Our test finds new iPad hits 116 degrees while running games | publisher=[[Consumer_Reports|Consumer Reports]] | date=March 20, 2012 | accessdate=March 22, 2012 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120322084359/http://news.consumerreports.org/electronics/2012/03/our-test-finds-new-ipad-hits-116-degrees-while-running-games.html | archive-date=2012-03-22 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>

=== 市場反應 ===
根據蘋果的媒體新聞稿，第三代[[iPad|iPad]]在發售的三天內賣出了三百萬部。 消費者對於第三代[[iPad|iPad]]的需求也被認為影響了[[掌上遊戲機|掌上遊戲機]]的銷售狀況，[[iPad|iPad]]的[[Retina顯示器|Retina顯示器]]和低價的[[遊戲|遊戲]]是造成此一影響的主因。<ref name="GameHeld">{{cite web | url=http://www.kitguru.net/channel/harrison/ipad-3-will-damage-handheld-console-sales-in-20122013/ | title=iPad 3 will damage handheld console sales in 2012/2013 | publisher=KitGuru | date=March 8, 2012 | accessdate=March 22, 2012 | author=Harrison | archive-date=2012-03-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120313141911/http://www.kitguru.net/channel/harrison/ipad-3-will-damage-handheld-console-sales-in-20122013/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

